      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Bruce W. Suter</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:182px;\"><a href=\"http://ieee-aess.org/contact/bruce-suter\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/a/a7/BruceWSuter.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:BruceWSuter.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Bruce W. Suter <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Bruce Wilsey Suter</b>,<br />\nan American mathematician, computer scientist, electrical engineer, and professor at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Air_Force_Research_Laboratory\">Air Force Research Laboratory</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rome_Laboratory\">Rome Laboratory</a>), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rome,_NY\">Rome, NY</a>. \nHis research interests include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Signal_processing\">signal</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_image_processing\">image processing</a> along with applications of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Compressed_sensing\">compressive sensing</a>\nand  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fast_Fourier_transform\">Fast Fourier transform</a>. Bruce W. Suter received a M.Sc. degree in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electrical_engineering\">electrical engineering</a> and Ph.D. in computer science from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_South_Florida\">University of South Florida</a> in 1972 and 1988 respectively, held visiting appointments at <a href=\"/Harvard_University\" title=\"Harvard University\">Harvard University</a> and the <a href=\"/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology\" title=\"Massachusetts Institute of Technology\">Massachusetts Institute of Technology</a>,\nand has also been with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honeywell\">Honeywell, Inc.</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Litton_Industries\">Litton Industries</a>, and the <a href=\"/University_of_Alabama_at_Birmingham\" title=\"University of Alabama at Birmingham\">University of Alabama at Birmingham</a>, where he was <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt's</a>  Ph.D. advisor on  <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallel search</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , and further co-authored with  Hyatt and <a href=\"/Harry_Nelson\" title=\"Harry Nelson\">Harry Nelson</a> on that topic <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1974_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1974 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1980_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1980 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1974_...\">1974 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1974 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>1974</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1672443\">The Modular Arithmetic of Arbitrarily Long Sequences of Digits</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOC\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computers</a>, Vol. 23, No. 12</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1980_...\">1980 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1980 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>1988</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=59711\">Some numerical applications of the radon transform</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_South_Florida\">University of South Florida</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a>, <a href=\"/Harry_Nelson\" title=\"Harry Nelson\">Harry Nelson</a> (<b>1989</b>). <i>A Parallel Alpha-Beta Tree Searching Algorithm</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.journals.elsevier.com/parallel-computing\">Parallel Computing</a>, Vol. 10, No. 3</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/r/Ruck:Dennis_W=\">Dennis W. Ruck</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://spie.org/profile/Steven.Rogers-5480?SSO=1\">Steven K. Rogers</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kabrisky:Matthew\">Matthew Kabrisky</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#MEOxley\" title=\"Mathematician\">Mark E. Oxley</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/80266\">The multilayer perceptron as an approximation to a Bayes optimal discriminant function</a></i>.  <a href=\"/IEEE#NN\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Neural Networks</a>, Vol. 1, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/80850\">Fast Nth-order Hankel transform algorithm</a></i>.  <a href=\"/IEEE#TSP\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=522979\">Multirate and Wavelet Signal Processing</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academic_Press\">Academic Press</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kdstevens.com/stevens/\">Kenneth S. Stevens</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998SPIE.3461...86S\">A Low Power, High Performance Approach for Time-Frequency/Time-Scale Computations</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SPIE\">SPIE</a> 3461, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kdstevens.com/~stevens/docs/spie98.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Han:Keesook_J=\">Keesook J. Han</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.spiedigitallibrary.org/conference-proceedings-of-spie/5108/0000/Low-bit-rate-enhanced-quality-JPEG-to-JPEG-2000-encoding/10.1117/12.487648.short?SSO=1\">Low-bit-rate enhanced quality JPEG to JPEG 2000 encoding</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SPIE\">SPIE</a> 5108, Visual Information Processing</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LixinShen\" title=\"Mathematician\">Lixin Shen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1155/2009/379402\">Bounds for Eigenvalues of Arrowhead Matrices and Their Applications to Hub Matrices and Wireless Communications</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asp-eurasipjournals.springeropen.com/\">EURASIP Journal on Advances in Signal Processing</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#NingChen\" title=\"Mathematician\">Ning Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#ZhiyuanYan\" title=\"Mathematician\">Zhiyuan Yan</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#MGadouleau\" title=\"Mathematician\">Maximilien Gadouleau</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/w/Wang:Ying\">Ying Wang</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Rank Metric Decoder Architectures for Random Linear Network Coding with Error Control</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/0909.4601\">arXiv:0909.4601</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/x/Xie:Hongmei\">Hongmei Xie</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#ZhiyuanYan\" title=\"Mathematician\">Zhiyuan Yan</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>General Linearized Polynomial Interpolation and Its Applications</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1104.3886\">arXiv:1104.3886</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#NingChen\" title=\"Mathematician\">Ning Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#ZhiyuanYan\" title=\"Mathematician\">Zhiyuan Yan</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#MGadouleau\" title=\"Mathematician\">Maximilien Gadouleau</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/w/Wang:Ying\">Ying Wang</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/5682080\">Rank Metric Decoder Architectures for Random Linear Network Coding with Error Control</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#VLSI\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Very Large Scale Integration (VLSI) Systems</a>, Vol. 20, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LixinShen\" title=\"Mathematician\">Lixin Shen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Blind One-Bit Compressive Sampling</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1302.1419\">arXiv:1302.1419</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LixinShen\" title=\"Mathematician\">Lixin Shen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1186/s13634-016-0369-4\">One-bit compressive sampling via ℓ 0 minimization</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asp-eurasipjournals.springeropen.com/\">EURASIP Journal on Advances in Signal Processing</a>, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.fr/citations?user=I5El37SUKxUC&amp;hl=en\">Trong Phong Nguyen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.irit.fr/~Edouard.Pauwels/\">Edouard Pauwels</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=rCH4toMAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Emile Richard</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce W. Suter</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i>Extragradient Method in Optimization: Convergence and Complexity</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1609.08177\">arXiv:1609.08177</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ieee-aess.org/contact/bruce-suter\">Bruce Suter | Aerospace &amp; Electronic Systems Society</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=fbQuez0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Bruce W. Suter - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=74279\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Bruce Suter</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_W._Suter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><